<HEADLINE> Spain Agrees to Train Police for Angola </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, December 19 (Xinhua) -- The Spanish government has
agreed to provide training and equipment to Angola's police in
the post-war era, police sources in Luanda said here today.
</P>
<P>
