resolve controversies regarding a small part of disputed mandates
at local elections, he said.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, tens of thousands of people continued their peaceful
march on Thursday through Belgrade in the 31st day of protests
against alleged Serbian government election fraud. The opposition
coalition Zajedno (Together) has organized all these rallies and
demonstrations, demanding the reinstatement of the annulled
election results.
</P>
