<HEADLINE> Role of Technology Stressed in Environmental Protection in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, December 20 (Xinhua) -- China will shift the focus of
its environmental protection movement from the current legal
emphasis to developing a comprehensive industry featuring new and
advanced technology.
</P>
<P>
State Councilor Song Jian made the remark during the three-day
national conference on technology for the environmental protection
system, which closed today in this north China port city.
</P>
<P>
"Good environmental protection, which is key to the achievement
of sustainable development, depends on legal measures, science and
technology, and development of the environmental protection
industry," Song said.
</P>
<P>
China has made remarkable achievements in environmental
protection through legal means, and now should stress science and
technology, he said.
</P>
<P>
To effectively deal with pollution, China's scientific and
technological research for environmental protection should mainly
control excessive pollution in major areas, and also monitor
manufacturing techniques that are environmentally-friendly, Song
said.
</P>
<P>
Research results should become practical applications, to be
carried out promptly and spread vigorously, he said, adding that
high and new technology of international advanced levels should be
adopted to tackle especially tough problems.
</P>
<P>
Song emphasized that scientific and technological development
should be guaranteed by designated funding.
</P>
<P>
"Apart from funding by the central and local governments, and
environmental protection departments, it is important to establish
a mechanism which guarantees that enterprises invest in
environmental protection under the socialist market economy," the
State Councilor observed.
</P>
<P>
He pointed out that to build the environmental protection
industry, China should introduce advanced technologies from abroad
and depend on its own enterprises with a relatively strong
strength in technology.
</P>
<P>
"Many large and medium-size enterprises can play an important
part in building the industry," Song said.
</P>
<P>
He urged scientific and technological workers to play a more
active role in spreading environmental protection awareness among
the people, and improving the nation's understanding of the
subject. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
