have come in for victims of snowstorms at the beginning of the
year in Qinghai Province.
</P>
<P>
Yushu Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture, the husbandry base in the
southern part of Qinghai, lost 1.3 million head of livestock, one
third of Qinghai's total. The animals of 2,199 local families were
all killed by the storm.
