<HEADLINE> Exhibition On Automobile Environmental Protection </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 20 (Xinhua) -- The '97 China International
Automobile Environmental Protection Technology Exhibition, the
first of its kind in the country, has been scheduled for May of
next year at the Beijing Exhibition Hall.
</P>
<P>
A symposium will be held simultaneously. At the time, experts
will discuss how to curb discharges by motor vehicles in China,
according to the "China Communications".
</P>
<P>
Exhibited will be low-pollution engines, discharge systems,
noise-control systems, oil supply and firing systems, maintenance
and test technology, and high-efficiency and energy-saving
equipment, the paper says. 
</P>
</TEXT>
