but Lindbom and Oberg denied Finland's chances with goals in the
last five minutes of the period.
</P>
<P>
Defending champions Russia got two goals from Oleg Belov. They
totally outplayed their young Canadian rivals. The victory was
the third for the host team in four days. 
</P>
